Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:24.12,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As quick as a veil of mist clears...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.12,0:00:25.88,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...we see through both love and cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.87,0:00:30.25,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A mysterious trick targeting a singer at his live performance finishing party!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.25,0:00:31.88,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:33.72,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:36.18,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.35,0:00:21.04,Signs,,0,0,0,,Poisoning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.68,0:00:03.39,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}"Poisoning."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.39,0:00:06.52,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}A way to take one's life through poison,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:09.48,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}where even the smallest dose is fatal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:11.74,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}When hidden in food or in a drink,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:15.49,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}it's almost impossible to escape from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:21.04,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So today, let's play back the case where I exposed a skillful poisoning trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.04,0:24:03.04,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A mysterious man delivered a sudden threat...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.04,0:24:05.17,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}"Leave the jewels alone?"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.17,0:24:06.25,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.25,0:24:10.21,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sorry, but you ain't stopping the one and only Kid so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.21,0:24:14.59,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The next target's the largest Indian Sapphire, the "Blue Birthday."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.59,0:24:16.22,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The night I announced the heist for is on Aoko's birthday,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.22,0:24:19.06,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}so I swore to myself I'd come back quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.06,0:24:21.47,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but then some weird guys attacked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.47,0:24:24.06,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What are these guys!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.06,0:24:33.49,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Detective Conan was brought to you by the following sponsors.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.08,0:24:44.04,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Next Kid's Magic: Moonlight
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.04,0:24:49.54,Signs,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.04,0:24:45.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next time, my beloved Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.83,0:24:47.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, what about Ky≈çgoku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.33,0:24:49.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's totally different.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:29.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why am I stuck with you guys\Nduring Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:31.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:33.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, what's up with Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:36.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He only calls once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:40.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's his problem?!\NChristmas only comes once a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:43.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's such a conceited mystery geek!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:48.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's always arrogant,\Nsnobbish, and mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:54.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But maybe that's what I like about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:55.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:59.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about you? Is there anyone you like, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:02.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course there is. Tatsuya Kimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tatsuya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:10.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, the guy from Lex,\Nthat rock band! Ta-tsu-ya Ki-mu-ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:15.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad got me invited to\None of their live performances!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:18.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get to see Tatsuya in the flesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:18.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wanna come, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:20.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're going to meet them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:23.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's the Suzuki Group's connections for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:25.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:27.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Sunday!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:29.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going, I'm totally going!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:40.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:45.03,Signs,,0,0,0,,Tatsuya Kimura (21)\NVocals
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:43.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:46.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Much better than some bands out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:50.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tatsuya! You've had too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:53.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know you have\Na talk show after this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:55.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shove it, ugly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:57.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ugly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:59.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's totally plastered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:03.13,Signs,,0,0,0,,Katsumi Yamada (21)\NDrums
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:03.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, Tatsuya, that's no way to talk to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:05.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mari's just doing her job as manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:12.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And have {\i1}you{\i0} been doing\Nyour job as our drummer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:15.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you, Mieko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:19.57,Signs,,0,0,0,,Mieko Shibazaki (20)\NGuitar
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was with you today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:20.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of your sucky playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:24.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Been waiting for you, Sumii{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:27.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had my manager reserve this for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:31.41,Signs,,0,0,0,,G≈ç Sumii (28)\NKaraoke Box Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:31.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks! I always\Nappreciate your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:34.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That said, it's sad that a former band leader
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:37.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is stuck running a joint like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:41.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- Shut up. Don't make me take this back.\N- {\i1}Former band leader{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:44.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? This song...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:46.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Rudolph the Red-Nosed Reindeer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I requested it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:51.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For you, Ms. Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:56.65,Signs,,0,0,0,,Mari Terahara (23)\NManager
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:56.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's perfect for you: you {\i1}did{\i0} believe in Santa
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:59.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,until middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:04.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you agree, Ms. Snooty Manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:06.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You jerk...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:09.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine. I'll sing your song.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.78,0:05:12.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later, Tatsuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:12.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:21.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, she's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:24.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it! What's he up to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:30.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's with that sad look?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:40.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, why's that lady crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I'm saying goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:46.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To both Mieko and the band.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:49.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're quitting Lex?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:53.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm leaving\Nwhen this tour's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:57.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone in the band knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:01.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good riddance to that hopeless drummer, that bratty guitar player,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and that snooty manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.46,0:06:08.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:16.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's my song!\NWho requested it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:20.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tatsuya, it's time to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:21.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're going to miss the talk show!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:25.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I'll sing whenever I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:26.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.94,0:06:30.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll call the studio to tell them we'll be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:35.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here we go! Bloody Venus!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:40.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Tatsuya Kimura passionately sang
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:43.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}his hit song, "Bloody Venus."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:47.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Nobody knew his voice
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:50.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}would never be heard again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:55.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Nobody... except his killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:01.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:04.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How was my song?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:05.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:07.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Katsumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.48,0:07:09.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gimme one of them rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:13.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:15.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:21.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you really quitting Lex?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:24.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, my solo debut's coming up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:25.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Solo debut?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:28.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My new song's already done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:30.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His new song's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:32.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...done?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:33.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's it called?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:36.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The title? It's called...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:42.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:43.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tatsuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:47.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tatsuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:55.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get an ambulance... Hurry, go get an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:55.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:03.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's no good! He's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:05.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That smells like cyanide!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:08.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Somebody planned this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:12.59,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who could've done this, right in front of me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:17.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The first suspect was Sumii,\Nthe guy who brought the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:20.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He and Tatsuya Kimura\Nused to be bandmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:25.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But then Tatsuya went pro\Nand became popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:27.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It looked like a jealousy murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:31.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But he was cleared of suspicion\Nwhen we learned
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:33.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}that everyone had eaten the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:40.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Furthermore, toxins were found on the\Nvictim's clothes and microphone,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:43.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}so he had touched the poison\Nbefore eating the rice ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:48.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Basically, the killer placed poison on the microphone
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:53.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,which indirectly adhered\Nto him when he grabbed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:57.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means it was done by\Nthe person who sang before him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:09:00.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...you, Mieko Shibazaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:06.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hear you sang a\Nfarewell song while crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:11.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen between you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:17.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tatsuya didn't dump me!\NHe turned me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:19.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mieko...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:22.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I told him how I felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:25.66,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sorry, Mieko. I already have someone I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:29.17,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She's gone right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:33.34,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but I'm waiting for her to come back. And she will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:35.97,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:38.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then to pay him back, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:41.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way! I didn't kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:42.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Someone he liked...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:47.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector. It was Tatsuya who requested\Nthe song that she sang!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:51.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She had no idea that\Nhe'd be singing next!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:55.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why she couldn't have\Npoisoned the microphone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:56.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That {\i1}is{\i0} true...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:10:02.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, who requested\Nhis Bloody Venus song?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:13.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, did Tatsuya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} always take\Nhis jacket off when he sang?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only at the start of every Bloody Venus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:19.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:24.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector! What part of his clothing\Nhad cyanide on it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:28.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His left elbow area, I believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:30.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On his staff jacket?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:34.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, there was nothing on his jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:38.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's it! Now I understand
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:42.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}how the killer poisoned Tatsuya Kimura!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:49.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And that killer is one of those three\Nwho have the same jacket on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:56.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, guitar lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:59.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The manager and Tatsuya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nwere arguing earlier;
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:02.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,were they always like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:06.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. They argued about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:09.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tatsuya always started it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:12.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's not as bad as he claimed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:16.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's smart, serious, and beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:18.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And she never caused any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:20.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:21.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:24.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found these in Tatsuya Kimura's locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:29.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't see anything useful here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:34.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A picture... A band picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:37.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's from when he and I had a band
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:39.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,before he went pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:43.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But only he and this person are still
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:45.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in the music industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:50.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wasn't the only one who left your band?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:53.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:57.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tatsuya said that person's why he wanted to quit...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:01.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that person's not in that picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:03.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, it's this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:05.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's really changed, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:07.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:10.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too much, if you ask me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:13.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's something written on the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:14.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lemme see it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:18.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:26.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But what a sad incident\Nthis is if it's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:35.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know who did it? How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:37.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. Okay. Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:43.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cancel the investigation!\NGet everyone back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:47.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:49.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:50.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"He?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:53.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A great detective you know very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:56.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi Kud≈ç.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:04.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Shin'ichi came back. He finally came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:06.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:15.10,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Welcome! Thank you all for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:17.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:21.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi Kud≈ç must be watching with this camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:23.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:24.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Shin'ichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:28.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's begin unraveling this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:29.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:33.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though, what's with this song?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:36.37,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's Rudolph the Red-Nosed Reindeer, Inspector Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:39.29,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's a Christmas song, it's played everywhere during Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:44.67,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It also stirred up the\Nkiller's hatred for the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:49.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, the killer is the one who Tatsuya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} requested this song for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:52.22,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes. Tatsuya{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s killer
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:55.52,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}was his manager,\NMari Terahara{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-san{\r\be10}! It was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:58.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}manager{\i0} killed him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:01.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:04.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop kidding around!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:08.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't even in\Nthe room when he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:13.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could've poisoned him\Ndespite your distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:15.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,simply by having him\Nsing this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:21.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was his hit song,\N"Bloody Venus!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:28.72,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Well, could you sing for us,\Nusing the mic I've prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:31.26,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's no poison on it, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:37.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine. I'll sing, if that'll make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:44.57,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Please wait! Why aren't you\Nremoving your jacket?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:49.78,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Tatsuya{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-san{\r\be10} always took his jacket off when he sang this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:51.57,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Isn't that right, people?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:52.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:54.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:00.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:02.71,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't forget the dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:16.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! She's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:18.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:24.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She used to sing with\NTatsuya in my band.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:30.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The manager...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:39.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, are you satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:42.00,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:45.96,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Now try eating\Nthe food I've prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:46.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:50.34,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just as Tatsuya{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-san{\r\be10} did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:51.76,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Pick whatever you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:55.35,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Assuming you can, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:16:02.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd rather not. I touched him\Nafter he collapsed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:06.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His hands and clothes\Nhad poison on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:09.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could've gotten\Nsome on my hands then, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:14.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then please check\Nher jacket, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:16.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her jacket?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:22.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Same goes for the jacket!\NI put it on after touching Tatsuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:25.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If there {\i1}is{\i0} poison on it,\Nthat doesn't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:30.00,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No. It's not poison\NI'm looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:35.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A lighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:35.76,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:41.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's Tatsuya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s missing lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:44.48,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In other words,\Nthat's not her jacket:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:49.11,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}she switched hers with Tatsuya{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s\Nto dispose of the evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:54.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wiped poison on the\Ninside of the left elbow
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:17:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so that some of it would\Nget on his shirt underneath
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:03.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when he put the jacket on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:07.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All that remained was\Nto have him sing Bloody Venus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:12.30,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}During his dance,\Nhe threw the jacket off
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:16.26,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and touched his left elbow with his right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:22.18,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Afterward, he died of poisoning\Nwhen he ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why would she do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:28.02,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Her motive is in the\Nphotograph on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:32.98,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's from when Tatsuya{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-san{\r\be10} was\Nin Sumii{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s band.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:36.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:39.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no one else in the picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:43.41,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She {\i0}is{\i1} there, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:47.37,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In the center of the picture,\Nwith Tatsuya{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-san{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:49.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can this be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.33,0:17:51.96,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's right. That picture\Nof her is the very motive
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:53.80,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}behind this murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:56.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:58.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! I had plastic surgery!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:17:59.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For Tatsuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:07.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I fell in love with him back then, when we were on the band...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:10.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So when he went pro...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:14.44,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come with me, Mari!\NYou can be my manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:17.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so happy when he said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:20.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought he felt\Nthe same way about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:24.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I got the surgery\Nto be worthy of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.99,0:18:28.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But his attitude suddenly\Nchanged after I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:31.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'd constantly call me ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:34.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He even had me sing\Nthe Rudolph song earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:38.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's{\i0} why he requested\Nthe song for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:42.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He made me his manager\Njust to insult me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:45.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I couldn't forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.01,0:18:46.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't forgive him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:50.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...because I loved him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:51.40,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You're wrong, Mari{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-san{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:56.90,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Tatsuya{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-san{\r\be10} had been in love\Nwith you for quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:59.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nonsense! What would you know about...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:19:03.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mari! He's telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:05.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector. Can I have that photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:10.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a love song he wrote about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:14.17,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"I want to talk with the real you"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:16.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't true!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:17.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:21.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those were the lyrics\Nto his newest song.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:24.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He always talked about you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:26.68,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why's Mari so self-conscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:30.10,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why'd she change her face for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:33.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he always treated me like...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:37.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wasn't good at expressing himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:40.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess he wanted the old you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:45.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't... It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:50.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:55.75,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm waiting for her to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:20:01.76,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sorry, Mieko. I already have someone I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:06.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The girl he liked was the manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:10.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tatsuya! Tatsuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:11.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tatsuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:23.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The combination of a man unable to express his feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:30.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and a woman who hid hers, brought forth a sad ending
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:33.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}in her weeping and tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:38.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Only her photograph sadly smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:07.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez. That's what you get for\Nusing the name "Shin'ichi Kud≈ç..."
